<li id="mwAtQ"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.justiceharvard.org" id="mwAtU">Justice: What's The Right Thing To Do?</a>, a series of 12 videos on the subject of justice by Harvard University's Michael Sandel, with reading materials and comments from participants.</li></ul>

